preference.name: CAETargetRefViewShownColumnNamePref
preference.preference_description: Stores the internal names of Item Revision properties which display names appear as columns from left-to-right in the Target References View in the CAE application. This preference value is only a repository, and it is not to be modified other than by the CAE Target References View code itself.
